{"tid":1291980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"昨日屯西地下屌爆個黃衫四眼呀叔","createTime":"2019-07-07T06:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T07:37:50.000Z","uid":115756,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"de649ac14cf21a7b7db068f101670c904542e4bf","tid":1291980,"uid":115756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:13:50.000Z","msg":"大概6點45 有個黃衫四眼呀叔 戴無線耳機<br />\n無啦啦指住人群大嗌: 你地班垃圾 係到搞事！<br />\n之後5秒內 就過百人圍撚住佢屌 <br />\n幾百個人圍住佢嗌佢 雞蟲！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後佢係咁叫人 打佢。 <br />\n但冇人郁佢 佢就係咁鳩走 想整啲身體碰撞 都係事敗<br />\n最後比人屌到走<br />\n<br />\n歷時不足一分鐘 就事敗<br />\n望住佢個樣 由原本好神氣 唔夠幾秒就比人屌到 落水狗咁好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好撚正！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230978bd527793672834cf660d5777ba17d4c57f","tid":1291980,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T06:39:41.000Z","msg":"有冇人有琴日康文署廢老打人 &amp; 警犬護送上的士既片? 我睇番琴日蘋果同立場既片搵唔到證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望有人可以幫手搵搵, 想試下send去廉政公署"},{"pid":"52525c6ba0190cc67eaa9eaa7f4f8e5d6c0962c7","tid":1291980,"uid":228438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"橙衫先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"504433ec00a33e475e580be4ec8427438cda7ed4","tid":1291980,"uid":52299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"應該要打佢 反正係佢自己要求"},{"pid":"c4cb1ea8e1036a1b296b8052054c116f75ab99cc","tid":1291980,"uid":235245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"504433ec00a33e475e580be4ec8427438cda7ed4","tid":1291980,"uid":52299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T07:27:15.000Z","msg":"應該要打佢 反正係佢自己要求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-